{"tid":1262643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］四港人闖軍營　解放軍報警","createTime":"2019-06-27T19:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T20:06:13.000Z","uid":260116,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32b21686c9ff75e7565f4599aa03a4591dac7c0a","tid":1262643,"uid":260116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:02:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20131228/18569627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20131228%2F18569627&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=ed6a403f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20131228%2F18569627&h=f80a6a88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20131228/18569627</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四港人闖軍營 解放軍報警</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KQFKBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KQFKBx.jpg&h=d4844658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「香港人優先」成員前日黃昏手持香港旗，「突襲」添馬艦解放軍駐港部隊總部，解放軍昨日報警。解放軍發言人向中通社表示，中環軍營是軍事禁區，四名香港市民不顧軍營營門哨兵警告，強行闖入軍營，涉嫌違反駐軍法、公安條例及受保護地方（保安）條例等。警方證實收到駐軍報案，會按既定程序處理，但沒透露案件歸類。<br />\n《駐軍法》第12條規定，香港駐軍以外人員如未獲駐軍最高指揮官或其授權軍官批准，不得進入軍事禁區。軍事禁區的警衞人員有權依法制止擅自闖入軍事禁區；破壞和危害軍事禁區的行為。特區政府亦應協助駐軍維護軍事禁區安全。<br />\n硬闖解放軍軍營是「香港人優先」快閃行動第一波，組織成員因不滿政府計劃將中環新海濱0.3公頃休憩用地修改為軍事用地及興建軍用碼頭，前日手持香港旗走進添馬艦解放軍總部大閘內，高叫口號反對有關規劃，並要求解放軍撤出香港。「香港人優先」成員招顯聰昨晚稱無懼被追究法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>純粹想問有沒有人知道佢地最後點樣？</ins>"},{"pid":"c27dd4a8518d510f486c231954641bdb01073127","tid":1262643,"uid":127447,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:26:00.000Z","msg":"個肥佬據聞呃綜援移民咗去台灣，<br />\n招顯聰消失於社運界，<br />\n個女嘅不知去向，相信亦已消失於社運界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181c0a0054d2fe626b86038da6d0b4916c379529","tid":1262643,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:27:35.000Z","msg":"13年己經咁有遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f40ccd7fb15fdf010bc9dd09825c4fca0d5e60e","tid":1262643,"uid":55758,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"92b4cc8162c4be83db7141a4482cf7a7cf34cb32","tid":1262643,"uid":35081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:47:59.000Z","msg":"組織成員因不滿政府計劃將中環新海濱0.3公頃休憩用地修改為軍事用地及興建軍用碼頭<br />\n<br />\n係咪依家話割果塊地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab370e299039d4e8f702bdc1bfaf1a71c328d2d3","tid":1262643,"uid":260116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92b4cc8162c4be83db7141a4482cf7a7cf34cb32","tid":1262643,"uid":35081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:47:59.000Z","msg":"組織成員因不滿政府計劃將中環新海濱0.3公頃休憩用地修改為軍事用地及興建軍用碼頭<br />\n<br />\n係咪依家話割果塊地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:48:23.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"09c2e0ebdc35b3e0dd95acb4d54efb8e6cfa8713","tid":1262643,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab370e299039d4e8f702bdc1bfaf1a71c328d2d3","tid":1262643,"uid":260116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92b4cc8162c4be83db7141a4482cf7a7cf34cb32","tid":1262643,"uid":35081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:47:59.000Z","msg":"組織成員因不滿政府計劃將中環新海濱0.3公頃休憩用地修改為軍事用地及興建軍用碼頭<br />\n<br />\n係咪依家話割果塊地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:48:23.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"仆街一早plan好左要送"},{"pid":"3cde3b04da735eca0fad59d6d744c18899d045bc","tid":1262643,"uid":260116,"like":3